data.description: Great Opportunity!!!! This 2-FAMILY DUPLEX is an irresistible opportunity for investors or a person that wants to live in the property, with an opportunity to rent the other unit. Offering great convenience & living space. Each side/side unit offers 3bdr, 1 full and 1 half bath. Each side has large bedrooms, Large Kitchen, formal dining area, and storage room in a full unfinished basement. These 2 units have their own private entry.  A separate driveway for two or more vehicles, complimenting ample parking available on the lot. This property is in a prime location with convenient access to access to route 23, shopping, &restaurants. Supermarket is walking distance, near schools and place of worship. This TWO-FAMILY DUPLEX has everything you need!!! also sellers' concession & FHA welcome. home sold as is
